{"tid":760061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港民族黨提五大要求   促交出對陳浩天的監視紀錄","createTime":"2018-07-29T07:48:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-29T09:59:02.000Z","uid":79563,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"5e66b83e6abeb1d38c2770a2684ac6260cdd6eff","tid":760061,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T07:48:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180729/large/1532842324_601f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180729%2Flarge%2F1532842324_601f.jpg&h=a1b7fc03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n保安局擬引用《社團條例》禁止香港民族黨繼續運作，民族黨原訂於下周二（8月7日）或之前提出書面申述，民族黨召集人陳浩天日前透露已透過律師去信保安局，要求將書面申述的限期延長至10月2日。保安局昨稱已收到信件，局方正處理有關要求。<br />\n<br />\n民族黨今天再在Facebook指，該黨與律師商討後，已於上周五（27日）向各方作出至少5點要求，包括要求保安局書面確認，並無與助理社團主任及其下屬於取締民族黨的建議書前，有任何有關通訊；若未能確認有關情況，則保安局須交出所有有關的口頭通訊的文件及紀錄。該黨同時要求助理社團主任於7月30日（周一）或之前，交出所有對陳浩天監視／觀察的記錄、預備取締建議書前及預備取締建議書時所收集的錄音及錄影，以及預備建議書時所有用及或無用及的資料。帖文未有說明各方若不回應有關要求，有何跟進。"},{"pid":"76890cc070a311d5861a55e84635a64cdff37807","tid":760061,"uid":34029,"like":4,"dislike":11,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:05:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 垃圾"},{"pid":"0334af1bba71a687e32ddc8ac2d308c3f14b13a1","tid":760061,"uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"留名等睇打手無限loop any of the following:<br />\n1，聲明<br />\n2，暴力呢/炸彈呢？<br />\n3，圈套<br />\n4，無論述/無條件/無可能<br />\n5，學獨聯私怨大爆炸"},{"pid":"bd3945532359df7807e21dbe4560a5e34b2fea4a","tid":760061,"uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:22:51.000Z","msg":"講返正題<br />\n保安局send九百幾頁文件，兩年監視紀錄，要民族黨幾個禮拜之內答覆<br />\n民族黨send返轉頭要保安局同警察幾日之內公開全部監視同內部通訊紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好似追劇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ebb5e69788de7dcfefa9c3ca9720b61b6d2ae5","tid":760061,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0334af1bba71a687e32ddc8ac2d308c3f14b13a1","tid":760061,"uid":131691,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T08:09:30.000Z","msg":"留名等睇打手無限loop any of the following:<br />\n1，聲明<br />\n2，暴力呢/炸彈呢？<br />\n3，圈套<br />\n4，無論述/無條件/無可能<br />\n5，學獨聯私怨大爆炸"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"講完竟然真係冇人loop<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3da0e05a1be8e2880c1ce1c20a7d8814fb1ee82e","tid":760061,"uid":72232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:49:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講返正題<br />\n保安局send九百幾頁文件，兩年監視紀錄，要民族黨幾個禮拜之內答覆<br />\n民族黨send返轉頭要保安局同警察幾日之內公開全部監視同內部通訊紀錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好似追劇咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有咩理據叫佢公開?"},{"pid":"357a7ac7676b59456c2438706f9ee0a5438df7f6","tid":760061,"uid":93940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:54:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港獨立</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcb6de44893f66f8ff9f5656a098186cdecafb12","tid":760061,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:55:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5db4d6e1573f2d5cdbc63991889c03c47f61f019","tid":760061,"uid":166474,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:55:58.000Z","msg":"阿仔教老豆扑野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24eefe9560e68242da93e3c3a1c751d043fc4509","tid":760061,"uid":176366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-29T09:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset